## Final Setup Instructions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **To make the feature fully operational, please update your `.env` file or environment variables with the following:**

### 1. EmailJS (OTP Verification)
Provide these from your EmailJS Dashboard:
- `VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID`
- `VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID`
- `VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY`

### 2. Google Sheets (Lead Collection)
1. Create a Google Sheet.
2. Go to **Extensions > Apps Script** and paste the code from the [Implementation Plan](file:///c:/Users/ALPHA-1/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2ceae481-7c1b-4e9c-bc2a-6108e006861d/implementation_plan.md).
3. **Deploy as Web App** (Access: "Anyone").
4. Add the URL to your project as:
    - `VITE_GOOGLE_SHEETS_CIBIL_URL`

